OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780938366
OL,3,CTata Steel expect delay to new Arc
OL,4,CFurnace due to electricity supply issue
OL,6,FA Tata Steel official has said that
OL,7,Fgetting the new Electric Arc Furnace
OL,8,F(EAF) operational at their Port Talbot
OL,9,Fsite could be delayed by up to 12
OL,10,Fmonths.
OL,12,FThe company's Executive Director said
OL,13,Fthe delay is due to an electricity
OL,14,Fsupply issue, but they are working
OL,15,Fwith the National Grid.
OL,17,FThe new #1.25bn EAF, which aims to
OL,18,Fcreate a greener way of steelmaking,
OL,19,Fis currently being built to replace
OL,20,Fthe former traditional blast furnaces.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
