OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780938366
OL,3,CTata Steel expect delay to new Arc
OL,4,CFurnace due to electricity supply issue
OL,6,FThe company had initially predicted
OL,7,Fthat the furnace would be operational
OL,8,Fby the end of 2027.
OL,10,FIn a call between Tata staff, Koushik
OL,11,FChatterjee, the Executive Director and
OL,12,FChief Financial Officer at Tata Steel,
OL,13,Fsaid they initially estimated an 18-
OL,14,Fmonth delay, which they have since
OL,15,Freduced to 12 months.
OL,17,FHe added that the company is working
OL,18,Fwith the government and National Grid
OL,19,Fand are hopeful to bring that delay
OL,20,Fdown further to "somewhere between six
OL,21,Fmonths and eight months".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780938366
OL,3,CTata Steel expect delay to new Arc
OL,4,CFurnace due to electricity supply issue
OL,6,FIn a statement, the National Grid
OL,7,Fsaid: "Construction is underway and
OL,8,Fgood progress is being made, and we
OL,9,Fhave been working constructively with
OL,10,FTata Steel and government to explore
OL,11,Foptions to accelerate the programme."
OL,13,FThe process to shut down Port Talbot's
OL,14,Fblast furnaces began in March 2024.
OL,15,FAround 2,000 jobs have been lost in
OL,16,Fthe move over to the EAF.
OL,18,FThe news of a delay comes at the same
OL,19,Ftime as a fire at the Port Talbot
OL,20,Fsite, which saw crews from 16 local
OL,21,Ffire stations sent to fight the blaze.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780938366
OL,3,CTata Steel expect delay to new Arc
OL,4,CFurnace due to electricity supply issue
OL,6,FThe fire broke out inside an
OL,7,Findustrial structure measuring
OL,8,Fapproximately 1,200 metres by 200
OL,9,Fmetres, housing the site's cold mill
OL,10,Fand pickle line operations.
OL,12,FReacting to the news of a delay and
OL,13,Fproblem with the electrical supply,
OL,14,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,15,Fsaid: "The national grid is
OL,16,Fsystematically failing businesses
OL,17,Fseeking to maintain and increase
OL,18,Femployment and expansion plans. This
OL,19,Fis yet another example of what is
OL,20,Fwrong with our privatised electricity
OL,21,Fsystem in Britain.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
