PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780938366
OL,3,CTata Steel expect delay to new Arc
OL,4,CFurnace due to electricity supply issue
OL,6,F"It acts only in the interests of its
OL,7,Fshareholders not the wider UK economy.
OL,8,FMaking eye watering profits that we
OL,9,Fcould be reaping the benefits from.
OL,11,F"Unite has raised this with
OL,12,Fgovernment. We need to renationalise
OL,13,Four energy starting with the grid."
OL,26,@uD@cO]
