PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780938366
OL,3,CTata Steel expect delay to new Arc
OL,4,CFurnace due to electricity supply issue
OL,6,FTata Steel said it has not made an
OL,7,Fofficial announcement of a delay yet
OL,8,Fhowever a spokesperson for the company
OL,9,Fsaid: "The Electric Arc Furnace
OL,10,Fprogramme is a major industrial
OL,11,Fproject and, like all projects of this
OL,12,Fscale, timelines continue to evolve as
OL,13,Fdetailed engineering, construction and
OL,14,Finfrastructure work progresses."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/6
